  schema:url &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/science/domains/biology/domains/botany/terms/solanum-lycopersicum/> ;
  schema:name "Solanum lycopersicum" ;
  schema:description "Herbaceous annual from Solanaceae; domesticated in Mexico 7000+ years ago. Produces indeterminate or determinate inflorescence patterns, triggering continuous or terminal fruit set. Characterized by buzz-pollinated hermaphrodite flowers, carotenoid and lycopene accumulation in ripening fruit, and twining stoloniferous root systems." ;
